<HEADLINE>
<P>
GALLERY: RAISING A RUCKUS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Raider fans. You can love them, leave them -- even arrest them.Followers of 
the Silver & Black have long believed in altering the team's motto of "A 
Commitment to Excellence" to "A Commitment to Rowdiness." And for the 13 
seasons since the team moved from Oakland to Los Angeles, "Just Win, Baby" has 
often become "Just Sin, Baby" in the Coliseum stands. But during a recent game 
against the New Orleans Saints, life was good, security high and intoxication 
of victory overshadowed that of the usual ne'er-do-wells. 
</P>
