A VOTE OF CONFIDENCE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 What a blessing it would be if Toby Muller's propositions could become law 
(Laugh Lines, "He's Got Propositions Too Hard to Refuse," Nov. 7) -- especially 
Proposition 261 for local news improvement (Moyer Law), Proposition 266 for 
holiday restrictions and Proposition 269 for junk mail/phone solicitation 
retribution. 
</P>
<P>
 I would crawl on my hands and knees to the polling place to vote for these. 
</P>
