<P>
 Making the final start of his career in the NYRA Mile on Saturday at Aqueduct, 
Bertrando virtually ran right off the plane.He didn't arrive in New York until 
Saturday morning and competed several hours later. 
</P>
<P>
 The 5-year-old Skywalker horse would have been better off if his flight had 
been delayed. 
