<P>
 Bertrando bowed out of the game with a whimper, finishing 10th of 12 in the 
$250,000 race, which was easily won by 8-1 shot Cigar. 
</P>
<P>
 Owned by Madeleine Paulson, trained by Bill Mott and ridden by Jerry Bailey, 
the 4-year-old Palace Music colt strolled home seven lengths in front of 2-1 
