<P>
 CORONA DEL MAR 03,17,09,08 1993-94 RECORDS OVERALL LEAGUE 11-13 5-9 COACH: 
Garth Flint 
</P>
<P>
 RECORD AT SCHOOL: 51-88 04,20,05,06,04 RETURNING STARTERS YR. HGT. P Shawna 
Casey Sr. 5-8 F Melissa Ford Jr. 5-6 G Kristy Macfarland Sr. 6-0 C 
04,20,05,06,04 TOP RETURNERS YR. HGT. P Ashley Conover Sr. 5-9 F Katie Thurman 
Sr. 5-11 F Lindsay Warmington So. 5-5 G 04,21,05,06,04 TOP NEWCOMERS YR. HGT. P 
