GIRLS' BASKETBALL 1994-1995: SEA VIEW LEAGUE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 IRVINE 03,17,09,08 1993-94 RECORDS OVERALL LEAGUE 10-14 4-10 COACH: Connie 
Brazell 
</P>
<P>
 RECORD AT SCHOOL: 13-48 04,20,05,06,04 RETURNING STARTERS YR. HGT. P Melinda 
Newe Sr. 5-8 G Shawnee Stevens Sr. 5-8 G 04,18,05,06,05 TOP RETURNERS YR. HGT. 
P Jenna Bodholdt Sr. 6-1 C Jennifer Kettner Sr. 6-0 F/C Sarah Usherwood Sr. 5-7 
