 Darwin Carter 
</P>
<P>
 School: Manual Arts 
</P>
<P>
 Height: 6-0 
</P>
<P>
 Position: Point guard 
</P>
<P>
 '93-94 Performance: Carter led the team in three-pointers made and was second 
in scoring at 16.4 points a game. 
</P>
<P>
 Buzz for '94-'95: Carter combines a good outside shot with extreme quickness. 
He is a good perimeter defender and is the strongest player on the team. Carter 
needs to improve his dribble penetration and must look to create for his 
teammates.  
