 Position: Shooting guard 
</P>
<P>
 '93-94 Performance: Howzell averaged 12 points a game on a Dorsey team that 
spread the wealth on offense. 
</P>
<P>
 Buzz for '94-'95: Howzell will be a focal point of Dorsey's perimeter game. He 
is the team's best three-point shooter and perhaps its best scorer. Howzell 
needs to look for better quality shots. Has good height for his position but a 
thin frame may result in fatigue after three quarters of physical play. 
