<HEADLINE>
<P>
JUST THE FACTS; THE COST OF FILM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Here's an average of what a 24-exposure roll of film costs in several cities 
around the world.Prices include sales tax and VAT where appropriate. 
</P>
<P>
 1. Tokyo: $5.75 
</P>
<P>
 2. Stockholm: $5.35 
</P>
<P>
 3. London: $5.27 
</P>
<P>
 4. Paris: $5.20 
</P>
<P>
 5. Milan: $4.64 
</P>
<P>
 6. Caracas: $4.20 
</P>
<P>
 7. Madrid: $4.13 
</P>
<P>
 8. Los Angeles: $4.03 
</P>
<P>
 9. Frankfurt: $4.02 
</P>
<P>
 10. Sydney: $3.86 
</P>
<P>
 11. Toronto: $3.55 
</P>
<P>
 12. Mexico City: $3.17 
</P>
<P>
 13. Sao Paulo: $3.08 
</P>
<P>
 14. Singapore: $3.08 
</P>
<P>
 15. Hong Kong: $2.59 
</P>
<P>
 Source: Runzheimer International 
