 Because the Spartans have no size, they will use a three-guard offense. Wolf, 
no relation to the coach, is the best player. The best hope for strength inside 
is Arneson, but he was injured during the last football game and may miss the 
start of the season. "This team has exceptional character," Wolf, the coach, 
