<HEADLINE>
<P>
PALM LATITUDES: VERBATIM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From the newsletter of the Beverly Hills-based Association for Astrological 
Networking: 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Hats Off To... 
</P>
<P>
 Regis Filbin, whose respectful use of astrology is consistently mentioned on 
his syndicated television program, Live! with Regis and Kathi Lee.Regis 
recently mentioned that during a business trip, he lost his wallet. "Mercury 
was in retrograde, you know!" he said. Also, he features an annual appearance 
on his show by his personal astrologer. 
</P>
<P>
 With phans like that... 
</P>
